==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Woundless
<hw>Wound"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from wound or
hurt; exempt from being wounded; invulnerable.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Knights
whose <xex>woundless</xex> armor rusts.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[Slander] may miss our name,⟦br⟧
And hit the woundless air.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Woundwort</ent>⟦br⟧
